<lb n="0572b17" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0572b18" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0572b19" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1665</head>
<lb n="0572b20" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0572004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此論宋本元本缺</note>金剛頂<note n="0572005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">瑜伽＝踰伽【和】＊</note><app n="0572005"><lem wit="【大】">瑜伽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">踰伽</rdg></app>中發阿耨多羅三
<lb n="0572b21" ed="T"/>藐三菩提心<note n="0572006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">論＋（一卷）【和】</note><app n="0572006"><lem wit="【大】">論</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">論一卷</rdg></app><note place="inline">亦名瑜伽總持<note n="0572007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">釋＝教【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0572007"><lem wit="【大】">釋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">教</rdg></app>門說菩提心觀行<note n="0572008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">修行＝修持【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0572008"><lem wit="【大】">修行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">修持</rdg></app>義</note></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0572b22" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0572b23" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0572009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（開府…智））三十三字＝（（唐））一字【明】，〔開府…智〕三十三字－【和】【內】</note><app word-count="33" n="0572009"><lem wit="【大】">開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿
<lb n="0572b24" ed="T"/>肅國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空
<lb n="0572b25" ed="T"/>諡大鑑正號大廣智</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唐</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】【內】">&lac;</rdg></app>大興善寺
<lb n="0572b26" ed="T"/>三藏沙門<note n="0572010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不空＋（阿闍梨）【和】</note><app n="0572010"><lem wit="【大】">不空</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">不空阿闍梨</rdg></app>奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0572b27" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT32p0572b2701">大<note n="0572011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔廣智〕－【和】【內】</note><app n="0572011"><lem wit="【大】">廣智</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】【內】">&lac;</rdg></app>阿闍<note n="0572012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">梨＝黎【明】【內】</note><app n="0572012"><lem wit="【大】">梨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【內】">黎</rdg></app>云。若有上根上智之人。不
<lb n="0572b28" ed="T"/>樂外道二乘法。有大度量。勇銳無惑者。宜
<lb n="0572b29" ed="T"/>修佛乘。當發如是心。我今志求阿耨多
<pb n="0572c" id="T32.1665.0572c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0572c01" ed="T"/>羅三藐三菩提不求餘果。誓心決定故。魔
<lb n="0572c02" ed="T"/>宮震動。十方諸佛皆悉證知。常在人天。受
<lb n="0572c03" ed="T"/>勝快樂。所生之處。憶持不忘若願成<app source="0572005" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">瑜伽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">踰伽</rdg></app>
<lb n="0572c04" ed="T"/>中諸菩薩身者。亦名發菩提心。何者<note n="0572013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">謂此＝謂次【明】，為次【和】【內】</note><note n="0572013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">謂此＝謂次【明】，＝為次【和】【內】</note><app n="0572013"><lem wit="【大】">謂此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">謂次</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】【內】">為次</rdg></app>
<lb n="0572c05" ed="T"/>諸尊。皆同大毘盧遮那佛身。如人貪名<note n="0572014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">官＝宦【明】【和】下同</note><app n="0572014"><lem wit="【大】">官</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】">宦</rdg></app>
<lb n="0572c06" ed="T"/>者發求名官心修理名官<note n="0572015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">行若＝若行【和】</note><app n="0572015"><lem wit="【大】">行。若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">若行</rdg></app>貪財寶
<lb n="0572c07" ed="T"/>者。發求財寶心。作經營財物行。凡人欲
<lb n="0572c08" ed="T"/><note n="0572016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">求＝為【和】【內】</note><app n="0572016"><lem wit="【大】">求</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】【內】">為</rdg></app>善之與惡。皆先標其心。而後成其
<lb n="0572c09" ed="T"/>志。所以求菩提者。發菩提心。修菩提行。
<lb n="0572c10" ed="T"/>既發如是心已。須知菩提心之行相。其行
<lb n="0572c11" ed="T"/>相者。三門分別。諸佛菩薩。昔在因地。發是
<lb n="0572c12" ed="T"/>心已。勝義。行願。三摩地為戒。乃至成佛。無
<lb n="0572c13" ed="T"/>時暫忘。<note n="0572017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唯＝惟【和】</note><app n="0572017"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">惟</rdg></app>真言法中。即身成佛故。是故說
<lb n="0572c14" ed="T"/>三摩地於諸教中。闕而不<note n="0572018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">言＝書【和】【內】</note><app n="0572018"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】【內】">書</rdg></app>。一者行願。
<lb n="0572c15" ed="T"/>二者勝義。三者三摩<note n="0572019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">地＋（法）【內】</note><app n="0572019"><lem wit="【大】">地</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【內】">地法</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0572c16" ed="T"/><p id="pT32p0572c1601">初行願者。<note n="0572020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">謂＝為【明】【和】</note><app n="0572020"><lem wit="【大】">謂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】">為</rdg></app>修習之人。常懷如是心。我當
<lb n="0572c17" ed="T"/>利益安樂無餘有情界。觀十方含識猶如
<lb n="0572c18" ed="T"/>己身。所言利益者。<note n="0572021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">謂＝為【明】【和】【內】＊</note><note n="0572021" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>謂＝為【明】【和】【內】＊</note><app n="0572021"><lem wit="【大】">謂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">為</rdg></app>勸發一切有情。悉令
<lb n="0572c19" ed="T"/>安住無上菩提。終不以二乘之法而令
<lb n="0572c20" ed="T"/>得度<note n="0572022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（今）＋真【內】</note><app n="0572022"><lem wit="【大】">真</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【內】">今真</rdg></app>言行人。<note n="0572023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（應）＋知【內】</note><app n="0572023"><lem wit="【大】">知</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【內】">應知</rdg></app>一切有情。皆含如來
<lb n="0572c21" ed="T"/>藏性皆<note n="0572024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">堪＋（任）【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0572024"><lem wit="【大】">堪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">堪任</rdg></app>安住無上菩提。是故不以二乘
<lb n="0572c22" ed="T"/>之法而令得度。故華嚴經云。無一眾生而
<lb n="0572c23" ed="T"/>不具<note n="0572025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔有〕－【和】，有＝足【內】</note><app n="0572025"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">&lac;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【內】">足</rdg></app><note n="0572026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">如來＝真如【和】【內】</note><app n="0572026"><lem wit="【大】">如來</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】【內】">真如</rdg></app>智慧。但以妄想顛倒執著
<lb n="0572c24" ed="T"/>而不證得。若離妄想。一切智。自然智。無礙
<lb n="0572c25" ed="T"/>智。則得現前。所言安樂者。謂行人。<note n="0572027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">即＝既【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0572027"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">既</rdg></app>知
<lb n="0572c26" ed="T"/>一切眾生畢竟成佛故。不敢輕慢。又於大
<lb n="0572c27" ed="T"/>悲門中。尤宜拯救。<note n="0572028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（隨）＋眾生【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0572028"><lem wit="【大】">眾生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">隨眾生</rdg></app><note n="0572029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔所求皆〕－【明】【和】，所求皆與＝願【內】</note><note n="0572029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">所求皆與＝願【內】，〔所求皆〕－【明】【和】</note><app n="0572029"><lem wit="【大】">所求皆與</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【內】">願</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】">與</rdg></app>而給付
<lb n="0572c28" ed="T"/>之。乃至身命而不&CB00385;惜<note n="0572030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">其命＝令其【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0572030"><lem wit="【大】">其命</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">令其</rdg></app>安存。使令悅
<lb n="0572c29" ed="T"/>樂。既親近已。信任師言。因其相親。亦可教
<pb n="0573a" id="T32.1665.0573a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0573a01" ed="T"/>導。眾生愚矇。不可強度。真言行者。方便引
<lb n="0573a02" ed="T"/><anchor id="fxT32p0573a01"/>進。</p>
<lb n="0573a03" ed="T"/><p id="pT32p0573a0301">二勝義者。觀一切法無自性。云何無自性。
<lb n="0573a04" ed="T"/>謂凡夫執著名聞利養資生之具。務以安身。
<lb n="0573a05" ed="T"/>恣行三毒五欲。真言行人誠可厭患誠可
<lb n="0573a06" ed="T"/>棄捨。又諸外道等。戀其身命。或助以藥物。
<lb n="0573a07" ed="T"/>得仙宮住壽。或復生天以為究竟。真言行
<lb n="0573a08" ed="T"/>人。應觀彼等業力若盡。未離三界煩惱尚
<lb n="0573a09" ed="T"/>存。宿殃未殄。惡念旋起。當<note n="0573001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">後＝彼【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0573001"><lem wit="【大】">後</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">彼</rdg></app>之時。沈淪
<lb n="0573a10" ed="T"/>苦海。難可出離。當知外道之法。亦同幻夢
<lb n="0573a11" ed="T"/>陽焰也。又二乘之人。聲聞執四諦法。緣覺
<lb n="0573a12" ed="T"/>執十二因緣。知四大五<note n="0573002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">陰＝蔭【和】</note><app n="0573002"><lem wit="【大】">陰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">蔭</rdg></app>畢竟磨滅。深起
<lb n="0573a13" ed="T"/>厭離。破眾生執。勤修本法。剋證其果。趣
<lb n="0573a14" ed="T"/><note n="0573003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">大＝本【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0573003"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">本</rdg></app><note n="0573004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">涅槃＝涅盤【和】</note><app n="0573004"><lem wit="【大】">涅槃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">涅盤</rdg></app>。<note n="0573005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以＝已【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0573005"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">已</rdg></app>為究竟。真言行者。當觀二
<lb n="0573a15" ed="T"/>乘之人。雖破人執猶有法執。但<note n="0573006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">靜＝淨【和】【內】</note><app n="0573006"><lem wit="【大】">靜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】【內】">淨</rdg></app>意
<lb n="0573a16" ed="T"/>識不知其他。<note n="0573007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">又＝久久【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0573007"><lem wit="【大】">又</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">久久</rdg></app>成果位。<note n="0573008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">已＝以【和】【內】</note><app n="0573008"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】【內】">以</rdg></app>灰身滅智。
<lb n="0573a17" ed="T"/>趣其涅槃。如<note n="0573009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">大＝太【和】【內】</note><app n="0573009"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】【內】">太</rdg></app>虛空湛然常寂。有定性
<lb n="0573a18" ed="T"/>者。難可發生。要待劫限等滿。方乃發生。若
<lb n="0573a19" ed="T"/>不定性者。無論劫限。遇緣便迴心向大。從
<lb n="0573a20" ed="T"/>化城起<note n="0573010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">為已＝以為【內】</note><app n="0573010"><lem wit="【大】">為<note n="0573011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">已＝以【明】【和】＊</note><note n="0573011" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>已＝以【明】【和】＊</note><app n="0573011"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】">以</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【內】">以為</rdg></app>超三界。謂宿信佛故。乃蒙
<lb n="0573a21" ed="T"/>諸佛<note n="0573012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">菩薩＋（加持力）【內】</note><app n="0573012"><lem wit="【大】">菩薩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【內】">菩薩加持力</rdg></app>而以方便。遂發大心。乃從初十
<lb n="0573a22" ed="T"/>信。下遍歷諸位。經三無數劫難行苦行。然
<lb n="0573a23" ed="T"/>得成佛。既知聲聞緣覺。智慧狹劣。亦不可
<lb n="0573a24" ed="T"/>樂。又有眾生。發大乘心。行菩薩行。於諸
<lb n="0573a25" ed="T"/>法門。無不遍修。復經三阿僧祇劫修六度
<lb n="0573a26" ed="T"/>萬行。皆悉具足。然證佛果。久遠而成。斯由
<lb n="0573a27" ed="T"/>所習法<note n="0573013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">散＝教【內】</note><app n="0573013"><lem wit="【大】">散</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【內】">教</rdg></app>致有次第。今真言行人。如前觀
<lb n="0573a28" ed="T"/>已。復發利益安樂無餘眾生界一切眾生
<lb n="0573a29" ed="T"/>心。以大悲決定。永超外道二乘境界。復修
<pb n="0573b" id="T32.1665.0573b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0573b01" ed="T"/><app source="0572005" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">瑜伽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">踰伽</rdg></app>勝上<note n="0573014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">法＋（人）【內】</note><app n="0573014"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【內】">法人</rdg></app>。能從凡入佛位者。亦超十
<lb n="0573b02" ed="T"/>地菩薩境界。又深知一切法無自性。云何
<lb n="0573b03" ed="T"/>無自性。前<note n="0573015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">已＝以【明】【內】＊</note><note n="0573015" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>已＝以【明】【內】＊</note><app n="0573015"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【內】">以</rdg></app><note n="0573016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（相說今以）＋旨陳【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0573016"><lem wit="【大】">旨陳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">相說今以旨陳</rdg></app>。夫迷途之法。從妄想
<lb n="0573b04" ed="T"/>生。乃至展轉。成無量無邊煩惱。輪迴<note n="0573017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">六趣者＝六趣【和】【內】</note><app n="0573017"><lem wit="【大】">六趣
<lb n="0573b05" ed="T"/>者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】【內】">六趣</rdg></app>。若覺悟已。妄想止除。種種法滅。故無自
<lb n="0573b06" ed="T"/>性。復次諸佛慈悲。從真起用。救攝眾生。應
<lb n="0573b07" ed="T"/>病與藥。施諸法門。隨其煩惱對治<note n="0573018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（迷津遇&CB00176;達於彼岸法亦應捨無自性故））十六字＝（（故無））二字【明】</note><app n="0573018"><lem wit="【大】">迷津
<lb n="0573b08" ed="T"/>遇&CB00176;達於彼岸。法<note n="0573019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">亦＝已【和】</note><app n="0573019"><lem wit="【大】">亦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">已</rdg></app>應捨。<note n="0573020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無自性故＝自性故無【和】</note><app n="0573020"><lem wit="【大】">無自性故</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">自性故無</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">故無</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0573b09" ed="T"/>如大毘盧遮那成佛經云。諸法無相。謂虛
<lb n="0573b10" ed="T"/>空相。作是觀已。名勝義菩提心。當知一切
<lb n="0573b11" ed="T"/>法空。<note n="0573021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">已＝以【明】</note><app n="0573021"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">以</rdg></app>悟法本無生。心體自如。不見身
<lb n="0573b12" ed="T"/>心。住於寂滅平等究竟真實之智。令無退
<lb n="0573b13" ed="T"/>失。妄心若起。知而勿隨。妄若息時。心源空
<lb n="0573b14" ed="T"/>寂。萬德斯具。妙用無窮。所以十方諸佛。以勝
<lb n="0573b15" ed="T"/>義行願為戒。但具此心者。能轉法輪。自他
<lb n="0573b16" ed="T"/>俱利。如華嚴經云。</p>
<lb n="0573b17" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT32p0573b1701"><l>悲<note n="0573022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">光＝先【明】【內】</note><app n="0573022"><lem wit="【大】">光</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【內】">先</rdg></app>慧為主</l><l>方便共相應</l>
<lb n="0573b18" ed="T"/><l>信解清淨心</l><l>如來無量力</l>
<lb n="0573b19" ed="T"/><l>無礙智現前</l><l>自悟不由他</l>
<lb n="0573b20" ed="T"/><l>具足同如來</l><l>發此最勝心</l>
<lb n="0573b21" ed="T"/><l>佛子始發生</l><l>如是妙寶心</l>
<lb n="0573b22" ed="T"/><l>則超凡夫位</l><l>入佛所行處</l>
<lb n="0573b23" ed="T"/><l>生在如來家</l><l>種族無<note n="0573023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">瑕＝暇【和】</note><app n="0573023"><lem wit="【大】">瑕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">暇</rdg></app>玷</l>
<lb n="0573b24" ed="T"/><l>與佛共平等</l><l>決成無上覺</l>
<lb n="0573b25" ed="T"/><l>纔生如是心</l><l>即得入初地</l>
<lb n="0573b26" ed="T"/><l>心樂不可動</l><l>譬如大山王</l></lg>
<lb n="0573b27" ed="T"/><p id="pT32p0573b2701">又准華嚴經云。從初地乃至十地。於地
<lb n="0573b28" ed="T"/>地中。皆以大悲為主。如無量壽觀經<note n="0573024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔云〕－【和】</note><app n="0573024"><lem wit="【大】">云</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">&lac;</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0573b29" ed="T"/>佛心者。大慈悲是。又涅槃經云。南無純陀。身
<pb n="0573c" id="T32.1665.0573c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0573c01" ed="T"/>雖人身。心同佛心。又云。</p>
<lb n="0573c02" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT32p0573c0201"><l>憐愍世間大醫王</l><l>身及智慧俱寂靜</l>
<lb n="0573c03" ed="T"/><l>無我法中有真我</l><l>是故敬禮無上尊</l>
<lb n="0573c04" ed="T"/><l>發心畢竟二無別</l><l>如是二心先心難</l>
<lb n="0573c05" ed="T"/><l>自未得度先度他</l><l>是故我禮初發心</l>
<lb n="0573c06" ed="T"/><l><note n="0573025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（初）＋發【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0573025"><lem wit="【大】">發</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">初發</rdg></app><note n="0573026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔心〕－【和】</note><app n="0573026"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0573027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔已〕－【明】</note><app n="0573027"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>為人天師</l><l>勝出聲聞及緣覺</l>
<lb n="0573c07" ed="T"/><l>如是發心過三界</l><l>是故得名最無上</l></lg>
<lb n="0573c08" ed="T"/><p id="pT32p0573c0801">如大毘盧遮那經云。菩提為因。大悲為根。
<lb n="0573c09" ed="T"/>方便為究竟。</p>
<lb n="0573c10" ed="T"/><p id="pT32p0573c1001">第三言三摩地者。真言行人如是觀已。云
<lb n="0573c11" ed="T"/>何能證無上菩提。當知法爾應住普賢大
<lb n="0573c12" ed="T"/>菩提心。一切眾生本有薩埵。為貪瞋癡煩惱
<lb n="0573c13" ed="T"/>之所縛故。諸佛大悲。以善巧智。說此甚深
<lb n="0573c14" ed="T"/>祕密<app source="0572005" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">瑜伽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">踰伽</rdg></app>。令修行<note n="0573028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔者〕－【和】</note><app n="0573028"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">&lac;</rdg></app>。於內心中。觀<note n="0573029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">白＝日【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0573029"><lem wit="【大】">白</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">日</rdg></app>月
<lb n="0573c15" ed="T"/>輪。由作此觀。照見本心。湛然清淨。猶如滿
<lb n="0573c16" ed="T"/>月光遍虛空無所分別。亦名<note n="0573030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（無）＋覺【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0573030"><lem wit="【大】">覺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">無覺</rdg></app>了。亦名
<lb n="0573c17" ed="T"/>淨法界。亦名實相般若波羅蜜海。能含種種
<lb n="0573c18" ed="T"/>無量珍寶三摩地猶如滿月潔白分明。何者。
<lb n="0573c19" ed="T"/>為一切有情。悉含普賢之心。我見自心。形
<lb n="0573c20" ed="T"/>如月輪。何故以月輪為喻。<note n="0573031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">謂＝為【和】</note><app n="0573031"><lem wit="【大】">謂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">為</rdg></app>滿月圓明
<lb n="0573c21" ed="T"/>體。則與菩提心相類。凡月輪有一十六分。
<lb n="0573c22" ed="T"/>喻瑜伽中金剛薩埵至金剛拳有十六大
<lb n="0573c23" ed="T"/>菩薩者。於三十七尊中。五方佛位。各表一
<lb n="0573c24" ed="T"/><note n="0573032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">智＋（也）【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0573032"><lem wit="【大】">智</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">智也</rdg></app>。東方阿&CB00434;佛。因<note n="0573033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">成大＝大成【和】</note><app n="0573033"><lem wit="【大】">成大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">大成</rdg></app>圓鏡智。亦名金
<lb n="0573c25" ed="T"/>剛智也。南方寶生佛。由成平等性智。亦名
<lb n="0573c26" ed="T"/>灌頂智也。西方阿彌陀佛。由成妙觀察智。
<lb n="0573c27" ed="T"/>亦名蓮華智。亦名轉法<note n="0573034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔輪〕－【和】</note><app n="0573034"><lem wit="【大】">輪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">&lac;</rdg></app>智<note n="0573035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔也〕－【和】</note><app n="0573035"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">&lac;</rdg></app>。北方不
<lb n="0573c28" ed="T"/>空成就佛。由成成所作智。亦名羯磨智也。
<lb n="0573c29" ed="T"/>中方毘盧遮那佛。由成法界智為本。已上
<pb n="0574a" id="T32.1665.0574a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0574a01" ed="T"/>四佛智出生四波羅蜜菩薩焉。四菩薩。即
<lb n="0574a02" ed="T"/><note n="0574001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">金寶法＝寶法金【和】</note><app n="0574001"><lem wit="【大】">金寶法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">寶法金</rdg></app>業也。三世一切諸<note n="0574002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">聖賢＝賢聖【明】</note><app n="0574002"><lem wit="【大】">聖賢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">賢聖</rdg></app>。生成養育
<lb n="0574a03" ed="T"/>之母。於是印成法界體性中。流出四佛也。
<lb n="0574a04" ed="T"/>四方如來。各攝四菩薩。東方阿&CB00434;佛攝四菩
<lb n="0574a05" ed="T"/>薩。<note n="0574003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔金剛〕－【和】</note><app n="0574003"><lem wit="【大】">金剛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">&lac;</rdg></app>薩埵。金剛王。金剛愛。<note n="0574004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（金剛）＋善哉【明】【內】</note><app n="0574004"><lem wit="【大】">善哉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【內】">金剛善哉</rdg></app>。為四
<lb n="0574a06" ed="T"/>菩薩也。南方寶生佛攝四菩薩。金剛寶。金
<lb n="0574a07" ed="T"/>剛光。金剛幢。金剛<note n="0574005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">笑＝&CB00764;【和】</note><app n="0574005"><lem wit="【大】">笑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">&CB00764;</rdg></app>。為四菩薩也。西方阿
<lb n="0574a08" ed="T"/>彌陀佛攝四菩薩。金剛法。金剛利。金剛因。
<lb n="0574a09" ed="T"/>金剛語。為四菩薩也。北方不空成就佛攝
<lb n="0574a10" ed="T"/>四菩薩。金剛業。金剛護。金剛<note n="0574006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">牙＝才【明】</note><app n="0574006"><lem wit="【大】">牙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">才</rdg></app>。金剛拳。為
<lb n="0574a11" ed="T"/>四菩薩也。四方佛各四菩薩。為十六大菩
<lb n="0574a12" ed="T"/>薩也。於三十七尊中。除五佛四波羅蜜及
<lb n="0574a13" ed="T"/>後四攝八供養。但取十六大菩薩為四方佛
<lb n="0574a14" ed="T"/>所攝也。又摩訶般若經中。內空至無性<note n="0574007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">自性空＝有性【和】</note><app n="0574007"><lem wit="【大】">自
<lb n="0574a15" ed="T"/>性空</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">有性</rdg></app>。亦有十六義。一切有情於心質中。有
<lb n="0574a16" ed="T"/>一分淨性。眾行皆備。其體極微妙。皎然明白。
<lb n="0574a17" ed="T"/>乃至輪迴六趣。<note n="0574008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">變＝亦【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0574008"><lem wit="【大】">變</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">亦</rdg></app>不變易。如月十六分之
<lb n="0574a18" ed="T"/>一。凡月其一分明相。若當合宿之際。但為日
<lb n="0574a19" ed="T"/>光。奪其明性。所以不現。後起月初。日日漸
<lb n="0574a20" ed="T"/>加。至十五日圓滿無礙。所以觀行者。初以
<lb n="0574a21" ed="T"/>阿字發起本心<note n="0574009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（之）＋中【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0574009"><lem wit="【大】">中</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">之中</rdg></app>分明。<note n="0574010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">即＝只【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0574010"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">只</rdg></app>漸令潔白分
<lb n="0574a22" ed="T"/>明。證無生智。夫阿字者。一切<note n="0574011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（諸）＋法【和】【內】</note><app n="0574011"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】【內】">諸法</rdg></app>本不生義。</p>
<lb n="0574a23" ed="T"/><p id="pT32p0574a2301">准毘盧遮那經疏釋阿字。具有五義。一者阿
<lb n="0574a24" ed="T"/>字<note place="inline">短聲</note>是菩提心。二阿字<note place="inline">引聲</note>是菩提<note n="0574012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">行＋（義）【內】</note><app n="0574012"><lem wit="【大】">行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【內】">行義</rdg></app>。三暗
<lb n="0574a25" ed="T"/>字<note place="inline"><note n="0574013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">長＝短【和】【內】</note><app n="0574013"><lem wit="【大】">長</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】【內】">短</rdg></app>聲</note>是證菩提義。四惡字<note place="inline">短聲</note>是般涅槃義。五
<lb n="0574a26" ed="T"/>惡字<note place="inline">引聲</note>是具足方便智義。又將阿字。配解法
<lb n="0574a27" ed="T"/>華經中開示悟入四字<note n="0574014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">也＋（開字者）【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0574014"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">也開字者</rdg></app>。開佛知見。<note n="0574015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（即）＋雙【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0574015"><lem wit="【大】">雙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">即雙</rdg></app>
<lb n="0574a28" ed="T"/>開菩提<note n="0574016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔涅槃〕－【和】，涅槃＝心【內】</note><app n="0574016"><lem wit="【大】">涅槃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">&lac;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【內】">心</rdg></app>如初阿字。是菩提心義也。示
<lb n="0574a29" ed="T"/>字者。示佛知見。如第二阿字。是菩提行義
<pb n="0574b" id="T32.1665.0574b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0574b01" ed="T"/>也。悟字者。悟佛知見。如第三暗字。是證菩
<lb n="0574b02" ed="T"/>提義也。入字者。入佛知見。如第四惡字。是
<lb n="0574b03" ed="T"/>般涅槃<note n="0574017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">義＋（也）【內】</note><app n="0574017"><lem wit="【大】">義</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【內】">義也</rdg></app>。總而言之。具足成就。第五惡字。
<lb n="0574b04" ed="T"/>是方便善巧智圓滿義也。</p>
<lb n="0574b05" ed="T"/><p id="pT32p0574b0501">即讚阿字是菩提心義。頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0574b06" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT32p0574b0601"><l>八葉白蓮一肘<note n="0574018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">門＝間【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0574018"><lem wit="【大】">門</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">間</rdg></app></l><l>炳現阿字素光色</l>
<lb n="0574b07" ed="T"/><l>禪智俱入金剛縛</l><l>召入如來寂靜智</l></lg>
<lb n="0574b08" ed="T"/><p id="pT32p0574b0801"><note n="0574019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">扶＝夫【明】</note><app n="0574019"><lem wit="【大】">扶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">夫</rdg></app>會阿字者。揩<note n="0574020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">實＝寔【和】【內】</note><app n="0574020"><lem wit="【大】">實</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】【內】">寔</rdg></app>決定觀之。當觀圓明
<lb n="0574b09" ed="T"/>淨識。若纔見者。則名見真勝義諦。若常見
<lb n="0574b10" ed="T"/>者。則入菩薩初地。若轉漸增長。則廓周法
<lb n="0574b11" ed="T"/>界。量等虛空。卷舒自在。當具一切智。凡修
<lb n="0574b12" ed="T"/>習<app source="0572005" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">瑜伽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">踰伽</rdg></app>觀行人。當須具修三密行。證悟五
<lb n="0574b13" ed="T"/>相成身義也。所言三密者。一身密者。如結
<lb n="0574b14" ed="T"/>契印召請聖眾是也。二語密者。如密誦真
<lb n="0574b15" ed="T"/>言<note n="0574021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（令）＋文【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0574021"><lem wit="【大】">文</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">令文</rdg></app><note n="0574022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">句＝字【明】</note><app n="0574022"><lem wit="【大】">句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">字</rdg></app>了了分明。無<note n="0574023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（一）＋謬【明】【內】</note><app n="0574023"><lem wit="【大】">謬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【內】">一謬</rdg></app><note n="0574024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">誤＝&CB00386;【和】，〔誤〕－【內】</note><app n="0574024"><lem wit="【大】">誤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">&CB00386;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【內】">&lac;</rdg></app>也。三意密
<lb n="0574b16" ed="T"/>者。如住瑜伽相應白淨月<note n="0574025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">圓＋（滿）【和】【內】</note><app n="0574025"><lem wit="【大】">圓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】【內】">圓滿</rdg></app>觀菩提<note n="0574026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">心＋（也）【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0574026"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">心也</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0574b17" ed="T"/><p id="pT32p0574b1701">次明五相成身者。一是通達心。二是菩提
<lb n="0574b18" ed="T"/>心。三是金剛心。四是金剛身。五是證無上菩
<lb n="0574b19" ed="T"/>提獲金剛堅固身也。然此五相具備方成本
<lb n="0574b20" ed="T"/>尊身也。其圓明則普賢身也。亦是普賢心也。
<lb n="0574b21" ed="T"/>與十方諸佛同之。亦乃三世修行證有前
<lb n="0574b22" ed="T"/>後。及達悟<note n="0574027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">也＝已【和】【內】</note><app n="0574027"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】【內】">已</rdg></app>無去來今。凡人心如合蓮
<lb n="0574b23" ed="T"/>華。佛心如滿月。此觀若成。十方國土。若淨
<lb n="0574b24" ed="T"/>若穢。六道含識。三乘行位。及三世國土成壞。
<lb n="0574b25" ed="T"/>眾生業差別。菩薩因地行相。三世諸佛。悉於
<lb n="0574b26" ed="T"/>中現證本尊身。滿足普賢一切行願故。大
<lb n="0574b27" ed="T"/>毘盧遮那經云。如是真實心。故佛所宣說。
<lb n="0574b28" ed="T"/>問前言二乘之人。有法執故。不得成佛。今
<lb n="0574b29" ed="T"/>復令修菩提心三摩地者。云何差別。答二
<pb n="0574c" id="T32.1665.0574c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0574c01" ed="T"/>乘之人。有法執故。久久證理。沈空滯寂。限
<lb n="0574c02" ed="T"/>以劫數。然發大心。又乘散善門中。經無數
<lb n="0574c03" ed="T"/>劫。是故足可厭離。不可依止。今真言行人。
<lb n="0574c04" ed="T"/>既破人法<note n="0574028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二＝上【和】【內】</note><app n="0574028"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】【內】">上</rdg></app>執。雖能正見真實之智。或
<lb n="0574c05" ed="T"/>為無始間隔。未能證於如來一切智<note n="0574029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">智＋（故）【和】【內】</note><app n="0574029"><lem wit="【大】">智</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】【內】">智故</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0574c06" ed="T"/>欲求妙道。修持次第。從凡入佛位者。即此
<lb n="0574c07" ed="T"/>三摩地者。能達諸佛自性。悟諸佛法身。證
<lb n="0574c08" ed="T"/>法界體性智。成大毘盧遮那佛。自性身。受用
<lb n="0574c09" ed="T"/>身。變化身。等流身<note n="0574030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔等流身〕－【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0574030"><lem wit="【大】">等流身</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">&lac;</rdg></app>。為行人。未證
<lb n="0574c10" ed="T"/>故。理宜修之。故大毘盧遮那經云。悉地從
<lb n="0574c11" ed="T"/>心生。如金剛頂瑜伽經說。一切義成就菩
<lb n="0574c12" ed="T"/>薩。初坐金剛座。取證無上道。遂蒙諸佛授
<lb n="0574c13" ed="T"/>此心地。然能證果。凡今之人。若心決定。如
<lb n="0574c14" ed="T"/>教修行。不起于座。三摩地現前。應是成就
<lb n="0574c15" ed="T"/>本尊之身。故大毘盧遮那經<note n="0574031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔云〕－【和】</note><app n="0574031"><lem wit="【大】">云</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">&lac;</rdg></app>供養次第法
<lb n="0574c16" ed="T"/>云。若無勢力廣增益。住法但觀菩提心。佛
<lb n="0574c17" ed="T"/>說此中具萬行。漸足<note n="0574032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">清＝淨【和】</note><app n="0574032"><lem wit="【大】">清</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【和】">淨</rdg></app>白純淨法也。此
<lb n="0574c18" ed="T"/>菩提心。能包藏一切諸佛功德法故。若修證
<lb n="0574c19" ed="T"/>出現。則為一切導師。若歸本則是密嚴國
<lb n="0574c20" ed="T"/>土不起于座能成一切<note n="0574033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（佛）＋事【明】【和】【內】</note><app n="0574033"><lem wit="【大】">事</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【和】【內】">佛事</rdg></app>。讚菩提心曰。</p>
<lb n="0574c21" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT32p0574c2101"><l>若人求佛慧</l><l>通達菩提心</l>
<lb n="0574c22" ed="T"/><l>父母所生身</l><l>速證大覺位</l></lg>
<lb n="0574c23" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>金剛頂瑜伽中發阿耨多羅三藐三菩提心論
